- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another likely category as the paper uses deep learning techniques for classification and description of dangerous situations. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also possible as the paper uses deep learning techniques for classification. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with detecting and communicating potentially dangerous situations.
